Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I care for and love our Hyeri very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what mistakes she makes, I want to cover for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, it's not really a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will organize it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A gangster kidnapped a high school girl named Kim Min-ji, and they both went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The gangster is missing, so now Kim Min-ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the student needs to disappear from the world.
